des:
Welcome to Disney Trivia! Kids and families can test their knowledge on everything Disney, from movies, to television, to music, to the Disney Parks and Resorts. 

One round of trivia is available to everyone.

You can unlock more rounds by purchasing the Pack of 120 Disney Trivia questions. Additional rounds are also available through Freetime Unlimited subscriptions.
